AddIncident: Improved location listening strategyThe previous implementation would often listen to only one provider. Forninstance, if GPS were enabled, getBestProvider would return gps fornboth the low and the high quality criteria. Now we explicitly attempt tonlisten to both the GPS and the Network provider, this way if GPS isnenabled, but the user is inside, we still have a chance of getting anfix from the network. This also ensures that if, say, GPS is enablednafter the activity started, we'll receive updates from it.nnIn addition, the last known location is retrieved and displayed whilenwaiting for a better fix.n
